  "description": "30 young men and women who came together on a shady bus tour. The tour's destination: an illusive, possibly nonexistent village called Nanakimura. In Nanakimura, one can lead a utopian existence, free of the world's obstacles … or so it was rumored, like an urban legend.<br>\n<br>\n\"In despair over the real world ... wanting to escape the tedious daily life … wanting to restart your life from scratch …\"<br>\n<br>\nThe bus headed deep into the mountains, carrying 30 people each harboring their own expectations and wounds in their hearts…<br>\n<br>\nAnd so, the place these 30 arrived at, was an uninhabited village with the lingering faint scents of life, even though it was falling apart.<br>\n<br>\nWhat is the truth of Nanakimura facing the 30? You can't miss even one episode!\n<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)",
